## ENFORCEMENT CHECKLIST

Before making ANY code change, verify:

- [ ] Is there a notebook for this code? (If no, create one first)
- [ ] Does the notebook contain implementation code? (Not imports from codebase)
- [ ] Have I written code directly in the notebook? (Not imported it)
- [ ] Have I removed any imports from codebase? (If they exist, remove them)
- [ ] Have I updated the notebook with my changes?
- [ ] Does the notebook pass all invariant checks?
- [ ] Have I extracted code from notebook to Python file?
- [ ] Have I verified the extraction worked?

**If any checkbox is unchecked, STOP and fix it before proceeding.**

